275:  *	   Query optimizer entry point
276:  *
277:  * To support loadable plugins that monitor or modify planner behavior,
278:  * we provide a hook variable that lets a plugin get control before and
279:  * after the standard planning process.  The plugin would normally call
280:  * standard_planner().
